Đêm hội nghệ_thuật Hành_động vì Khí_hậu Power_Up đã nhận được sự đồng_hành và hỗ_trợ của các đối_tác sau : Quỹ_Global_Greengrants_Fund , Tập_đoàn Dragon_Capital , Đại_sứ_quán Đức , Lãnh_sự_quán Pháp , Trung_tâm LIN , Quỹ EXO Foundation , Học_viện Âm_nhạc và Nghệ_thuật Biểu_diễn SOUL , RABBAT , TicketBox , Cargo_Bar , Think in a Box và Dancenter .
- - - - - - - - - - - - - - -
For the first time , an epic Climate_Action_Festival under the name POWER_UP organised by CHANGE ( changevn.org ) and 350.org Vietnam will occur with plenty of captivating and exciting activities for young people to respond to the United_Nations_Climate_Change_Conference COP21 happening at the end of November and the beginning of December in Paris . Let ’ s see what you ’ ll get from participating in this biggest environmental event of the year !
- Meet , interact and immerse yourself in an energetic and trendy music atmosphere of EDM , powerful ambience of Rock , and a lively feel of different art forms with Thanh_Bui , Uyen_Linh , Vu_Cat_Tuong , Tien_Tien , Bich_Ngoc , Thao_Trang , Mai_Khoi , Nguyen_Dinh_Thanh_Tam , Ha_Okio , Tang_Nhat_Tue , My_Le , 5 Dong_Ke , Rapper_Tien_Dat , The_Rock_Band PAK , DJ Duc_Thien and MC Nguyet_Anh .
- Experience various interesting environmental corners to find out more about coal , meet the Coal_Witch ; create a field of pinwheels , watch wedding scenes between the Earth and Renewable_Energy ; see meaningful films about environment for FREE ; challenge yourself with fun games about the environment ; … as well as many , many other exhilarating activities which will not leave you still .
- And last but not least , to engage with thousands of other young people who also love the environment at Cargo , which will be filled with NEON colours to respond and send powerful messages from Vietnam youth to COP21 . Remember to dress in NEON-colour clothing and accessories to not be “ left out ” , guys !
Time : 16 : 00 – 21 : 00 , Wednesday 25.11.2015
Location : CARGO Event_Space , 7 Nguyen_Tat_Thanh_Street , District 4 , Ho_Chi_Minh_City ( Khanh_Hoi bridge )
Ticket price * :
30,000 VND/ticket ( ONLY for the first 300 tickets )
50,000 VND/ticket ( for the 301st ticket till sold out )
( * All money generated from the selling of tickets will be donated to CHANGE’ s Protecting and Coping with Climate_Change fund )
Buy tickets at :
- Ticketbox.vn ( http : / / bit.ly/powerupvn )
- Buy directly at universities in Ho_Chi_Minh_City ( list of universities to be confirmed )
- Or at CHANGE office , 5th Floor , 132-134 D2 Street , Ward 25 , Binh_Thanh_District , Ho_Chi_Minh_City .
Hotline : 0165.425.8897 | ( 08 ) 6681 3513 ( Mr . Ân )
What are you waiting for ? ! Grab those first tickets to participate in a leading environmental event and share information , bring your friends , so you can save the environment together !
